@Reckon.PointOfSale.WebApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5238

### Post a UserCreated event
POST {{Reckon.PointOfSale.WebApi_HostAddress}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "UserCreated",
  "payload": {
    "userId": "usr-001",
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane@example.com"
  },
  "timestamp": "2025-01-15T10:30:00Z"
}

### Post an OrderPlaced event
POST {{Reckon.PointOfSale.WebApi_HostAddress}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "OrderPlaced",
  "payload": {
    "orderId": "ord-100",
    "amount": 49.95,
    "currency": "AUD"
  },
  "timestamp": "2025-01-15T11:00:00Z"
}

### Post an unknown event (handled by FallbackHandler)
POST {{Reckon.PointOfSale.WebApi_HostAddress}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "InventoryAdjusted",
  "payload": {
    "sku": "SKU-999",
    "delta": -3
  },
  "timestamp": "2025-01-15T12:00:00Z"
}

### Post an invalid event (missing eventType — returns validation error)
POST {{Reckon.PointOfSale.WebApi_HostAddress}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": { "data": "test" },
  "timestamp": "2025-01-15T12:00:00Z"
}

### Get all events
GET {{Reckon.PointOfSale.WebApi_HostAddress}}/events

### Get a single event by ID (replace with a real ID from a previous POST response)
GET {{Reckon.PointOfSale.WebApi_HostAddress}}/events/e1244140-e42c-44c4-b962-33aaaebf253f
